      "sc:description": "EU-PEARL is a framework and open-source software suite for designing and simulating platform clinical trials, particularly for paediatric neurofibromatosis-1 and schwannomatosis. It addresses limitations of existing software and enables iterative design optimization through simulation.",
      "sc:featureList": {
        "@id": "edam:operation_4009"
      },
      "sc:name": "EU-PEARL Simulation Framework",
